   "body" : "`CScheduler::serviceQueue` has the following code:\r\n\r\n```\r\n+            lock.unlock();\r\n+            f();\r\n+            lock.lock();\r\n+        } catch (...) {\r\n+            --nThreadsServicingQueue;\r\n+            throw;\r\n+        }\r\n```\r\n\r\nIn case `f` throws the statement `--nThreadsServicingQueue;` will run while not protected by the lock. This is a race condition and UB.",
